parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the EPS system can cause the power steering to stop working, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The power steering warning light is illuminated
the steering wheel becomes stiff or hard to turn
the vehicle shakes or vibrates
the power steering assist motor fails
the steering wheel locks up
the vehicle is difficult to maneuver
and the EPS system fails intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the power steering to stop working, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering wheel becomes stiff or hard to turn
the power steering assist motor fails
the steering wheel locks up
the vehicle is difficult to maneuver
and the EPS system fails intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering pump can cause the power steering to stop working, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The power steering warning light is illuminated
the steering wheel becomes stiff or hard to turn
the vehicle shakes or vibrates
and the power steering assist motor fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various malfunctions, including stalling, loss of power, and failure of essential systems, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The instrument panel lights flash on and off
the speedometer gauge fails to indicate the actual speed of the vehicle
the battery warning indicator illuminates
the power steering and headlights malfunction
and the doors independently lock while the engine is running.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The key fails to turn in the ignition
the security light comes on
the vehicle stalls without warning
and the ignition switch turns on without the key being turned.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The fuel gauge malfunctions
the fuel pump fails
the vehicle stalls without warning
and the check engine light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause loss of control, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The brake lights malfunction
the brake pedal travels to the floorboard
and the traction control light becomes illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the security system can cause the vehicle to not start or stall, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The security light comes on
the vehicle fails to start
and the ignition switch turns on without the key being turned.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the headlights to malfunction, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Headlights fail to illuminate
dim
or flicker; excessive heat conductivity within the system; bulbs melt or destroy connections; headlights turn off and on randomly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the brake lights can cause confusion and accidents, as other drivers may not be aware of the vehicle's intentions.
symptoms: Brake lights illuminate without the brake pedal being pressed; brake lights do not illuminate when the brake pedal is pressed; brake lights flash on and off intermittently; brake lights stay on when the vehicle is in motion or stationary.
